{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ After this creature attacks, draw up to 2 cards, then discard a card from your hand. If you discard a card that has "Momoking" in its name, untap this creature. If you discard a RexStars in this way, choose one of your opponent's creatures and return it to its owner's hand.
